                android:text="A line follower robot basically follows a line. It uses the principle that Black color reflects less light falling on it as compare to the White color.
We can use IR-LED sensors or LDR sensors to measure and compare the intensity of reflected light.
"
                android:textColor="#ccffffff"
                android:padding="10dp"
